snippet.title: Rayman Designer Level: Sugar Rush
snippet.description:
Rayman Designer Level: Sugar Rush
This is a brand new level i have creating using the rayman designer game which was released for pc in 1997. To complete the level you must collect all 100 blue tings as this will make the exit appear. the coloured tings are just to make other objects appear. 

rayman designer forum: http://z15.invisionfree.com/Tehrunescape455/index.php?s=7fc153170a1270977d00fd6d5a9f655a&act=idx   

Download the Level here: 
https://app.box.com/s/nlhtd2oia1yeuri3xeoggqmk4txpqo7x 

enjoy the vid 
------------------------
classicgamerx11
